data.expected_result: Always get redirected to the page
data.short_description: [Website Bug] When you go to the rich presence site via Canary, sometimes you get a 404 error when you click "Get Started"
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to https://canary/(dot)discordapp(dot)com/rich-presence - Click on either of the Get Started buttons either in the bottom or the first button on the page - If you weren't able to reproduce, try a few times, it can take a couple of tries
